logs/*.log
logs/auto-publish-state.json

# Local Codex/agent session artifacts; must never make the working tree dirty.
# An untracked .context/ was tripping auto-sync's pre-rebase guard and blocking pushes.
.context/

# Guard against fallback scripts ever writing markdown to content/ top-level.
# All site content must live in subdirectories (daily-ai-news, weekly-ai-tech, portfolio-news).
content/*.md
!content/README.md
